1
00:00:58,760 --> 00:01:00,040
What we damaged the most this time

2
00:01:00,040 --> 00:01:01,560
are the fresh goji berries.

3
00:01:01,560 --> 00:01:03,720
For other goji berry products,

4
00:01:03,760 --> 00:01:05,840
we just need to upgrade the original packaging.

5
00:01:05,840 --> 00:01:08,240
I want to change the packaging for the fresh goji berries

6
00:01:08,240 --> 00:01:09,680
to this. Take a look.

7
00:01:11,760 --> 00:01:13,020
It's EPE pearl cotton.

8
00:01:13,240 --> 00:01:15,080
It's waterproof, moisture-proof, and highly resilient.

9
00:01:15,080 --> 00:01:15,920
Most importantly,

10
00:01:15,920 --> 00:01:17,480
it has excellent shock resistance.

11
00:01:17,480 --> 00:01:18,880
It's pressure-resistant and shatterproof.

12
00:01:18,880 --> 00:01:21,280
If we add a foam plastic box on the outside,

13
00:01:21,440 --> 00:01:22,770
it should be foolproof.

14
00:01:23,120 --> 00:01:24,850
How much did the cost increase?

15
00:01:24,960 --> 00:01:25,800
Five percent.

16
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:27,960
That's not low.

17
00:01:28,440 --> 00:01:30,280
However, it looks like it's a third smaller

18
00:01:30,280 --> 00:01:31,940
than the original packaging.

19
00:01:32,400 --> 00:01:34,800
Maybe we can cut some of the shipping costs.

20
00:01:35,360 --> 00:01:36,680
Moving forward, for every step,

21
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:37,720
we must ensure

22
00:01:37,720 --> 00:01:39,000
that there are no more mistakes.

23
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:41,460
I'm also talking to a new logistics company.

24
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:42,560
Lao Liu's side

25
00:01:42,720 --> 00:01:44,979
does have a problem with rough handling.

26
00:01:45,120 --> 00:01:45,720
It's okay.

27
00:01:45,880 --> 00:01:46,920
Yesterday, I contacted

28
00:01:46,920 --> 00:01:49,080
a logistics company we worked with before.

29
00:01:49,080 --> 00:01:51,600
Their logistics capacity is probably in the top three nationwide.

30
00:01:51,600 --> 00:01:52,600
I asked around,

31
00:01:52,759 --> 00:01:55,090
and they just set up a branch in our county.

32
00:01:55,560 --> 00:01:56,360
How about this?

33
00:01:56,360 --> 00:01:57,240
Tomorrow, the two of us

34
00:01:57,240 --> 00:01:59,280
will go visit the branch boss together.

35
00:01:59,280 --> 00:02:00,880
Let's try to get a negotiated price.

36
00:02:00,880 --> 00:02:01,480
Okay.

37
00:02:01,880 --> 00:02:03,240
I'll also look into

38
00:02:03,480 --> 00:02:06,140
the government's logistics subsidy policies.

39
00:02:07,320 --> 00:02:08,919
That's great.

40
00:02:09,560 --> 00:02:10,880
Brother Secretary and Sister Renzhen

41
00:02:10,880 --> 00:02:12,600
were both shining just now.

42
00:02:13,640 --> 00:02:14,560
Get to work.

43
00:02:18,600 --> 00:02:19,329
How did it go?

44
00:02:19,600 --> 00:02:20,600
I asked their staff.

45
00:02:20,600 --> 00:02:22,560
They said the boss doesn't come here often,

46
00:02:22,560 --> 00:02:24,560
but Manager Chen gave me an address.

47
00:02:24,680 --> 00:02:25,680
I know this place.

48
00:02:25,680 --> 00:02:26,280
Let's go.

49
00:02:35,280 --> 00:02:35,880
Mr. Li,

50
00:02:36,040 --> 00:02:37,440
sorry to bother you.

51
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:39,600
You are...

52
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:41,960
from Xia Village?

53
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:44,360
I'm the head of e-commerce for Xia Village,

54
00:02:44,360 --> 00:02:45,079
Ren Zhen.

55
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:47,120
This is our Secretary, Jiao Li.

56
00:02:47,760 --> 00:02:50,360
Manager Chen should have told you everything.

57
00:02:50,880 --> 00:02:52,720
My friend and I are eating right now.

58
00:02:52,720 --> 00:02:53,440
But,

59
00:02:53,680 --> 00:02:54,920
visitors are always welcome.

60
00:02:54,920 --> 00:02:56,520
Sit down. Let's eat and talk.

61
00:02:56,960 --> 00:02:57,520
Okay.

62
00:02:57,880 --> 00:02:58,540
Have a seat.

63
00:03:03,280 --> 00:03:05,760
Mr. Li, our Xiacun Village grows goji berries,

64
00:03:05,760 --> 00:03:06,440
and we have also cooperated with factories

65
00:03:06,440 --> 00:03:08,500
to develop some goji berry products.

66
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:11,880
Our village is currently developing a live-streaming business.

67
00:03:11,880 --> 00:03:14,160
We're hoping to partner with your Jiangda Express

68
00:03:14,160 --> 00:03:15,280
for fresh fruit logistics.

69
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:16,240
We just got here,

70
00:03:16,480 --> 00:03:20,140
and you're already talking about work before even having a drink?

71
00:03:22,600 --> 00:03:24,329
Drink this glass of wine first.

72
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:29,560
I remember regarding the logistics,

73
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:31,290
Miss Ren wanted to talk with me.

74
00:03:31,640 --> 00:03:32,600
So this wine

75
00:03:33,680 --> 00:03:35,320
should be for Miss Ren to drink.

76
00:03:35,320 --> 00:03:35,960
Right?

77
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:37,320
Okay, no problem.

78
00:03:39,720 --> 00:03:40,240
Don't.

79
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:44,360
Straightforward.

80
00:03:45,880 --> 00:03:46,640
However,

81
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:48,260
you guys are a bit late.

82
00:03:48,320 --> 00:03:50,000
We're already halfway through the meal.

83
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:51,079
In Xinjiang,

84
00:03:51,280 --> 00:03:52,880
there's a rule for drinking.

85
00:03:52,960 --> 00:03:54,760
Those who join halfway

86
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:56,480
must be penalized with a drink.

87
00:03:56,480 --> 00:03:58,280
Yes, yes, I should be penalized.

88
00:03:58,360 --> 00:03:59,420
Ren Zhen, let's go.

89
00:04:00,200 --> 00:04:01,360
Don't worry.

90
00:04:01,520 --> 00:04:03,000
Sit down. I can handle it.

91
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:06,220
Are we still drinking?

92
00:04:08,200 --> 00:04:08,760
Mr. Li,

93
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:11,280
I will definitely make sure you drink happily today.

94
00:04:11,280 --> 00:04:12,760
But before we drink,

95
00:04:12,920 --> 00:04:14,640
I sincerely want to

96
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:15,720
say a few words

97
00:04:15,840 --> 00:04:17,040
about our business.

98
00:04:17,440 --> 00:04:18,300
It's like this.

99
00:04:18,320 --> 00:04:20,240
Our Xiacun account

100
00:04:20,399 --> 00:04:22,600
currently has 200,000 followers across all platforms.

101
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:24,400
In every live stream, it takes less than ten minutes

102
00:04:24,400 --> 00:04:25,930
for everything to sell out.

103
00:04:25,960 --> 00:04:27,280
So this time, the two of us

104
00:04:27,280 --> 00:04:28,400
are mainly here to discuss

105
00:04:28,400 --> 00:04:30,280
a long-term partnership with you.

106
00:04:30,280 --> 00:04:31,200
In future live streams,

107
00:04:31,200 --> 00:04:32,720
we can not only sell goji berries

108
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:35,000
but also local specialties from surrounding counties and cities.

109
00:04:35,000 --> 00:04:36,560
Everything can be put on the table.

110
00:04:36,560 --> 00:04:37,720
By then, the shipping volume

111
00:04:37,720 --> 00:04:39,640
will be more than five times what it is now.

112
00:04:39,640 --> 00:04:40,159
Mr. Li,

113
00:04:40,280 --> 00:04:42,680
do you think there is still room

114
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:44,200
for negotiation?

115
00:04:44,360 --> 00:04:45,320
As for me,

116
00:04:45,560 --> 00:04:47,890
I hate it when people make empty promises.

117
00:04:48,560 --> 00:04:51,159
If you want a full stomach, you have to eat naan.

118
00:04:51,800 --> 00:04:53,680
You are friends with Manager Chen,

119
00:04:53,680 --> 00:04:55,880
but Jiangda Express's branch contractors

120
00:04:55,880 --> 00:04:57,320
are individual contractors.

121
00:04:57,320 --> 00:04:59,360
We are responsible for our own profits and losses.

122
00:04:59,360 --> 00:05:00,880
I have to make money too.

123
00:05:01,760 --> 00:05:02,400
Yes.

124
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:05,360
If we have a good chat today,

125
00:05:05,760 --> 00:05:07,690
I might consider the agreed price.

126
00:05:07,880 --> 00:05:08,610
Understood.

127
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:09,880
Then I'll offer

128
00:05:10,080 --> 00:05:11,280
Mr. Li another toast.

129
00:05:12,960 --> 00:05:14,890
I'll finish mine, you take it easy.

130
00:05:29,640 --> 00:05:30,280
Mr. Li,

131
00:05:30,400 --> 00:05:32,280
am I qualified to talk to you now?

132
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:33,680
Go ahead.

133
00:05:39,720 --> 00:05:41,159
Drinking by the rules

134
00:05:41,280 --> 00:05:42,409
shows my sincerity.

135
00:05:42,880 --> 00:05:45,520
But I definitely won't use it as a stepping stone.

136
00:05:45,520 --> 00:05:47,850
This is the document for our agreed price.

137
00:05:48,840 --> 00:05:50,560
Mr. Li, you can take a close look

138
00:05:50,560 --> 00:05:52,600
to see if we're making empty promises.

139
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:53,920
The details of the agreed price

140
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:55,600
and our Party Secretary's contact info

141
00:05:55,600 --> 00:05:56,600
are all in the document.

142
00:05:56,600 --> 00:05:57,659
Our Secretary said

143
00:05:57,680 --> 00:05:58,480
at this price,

144
00:05:58,480 --> 00:06:00,210
you definitely won't lose out.

145
00:06:01,040 --> 00:06:01,560
Right.

146
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:02,400
Also,

147
00:06:06,200 --> 00:06:07,320
This is Xia Village's

148
00:06:07,320 --> 00:06:09,560
growth chart for live streaming e-commerce.

149
00:06:09,560 --> 00:06:10,640
And here's the proposal.

150
00:06:10,640 --> 00:06:11,280
Mr. Li,

151
00:06:11,440 --> 00:06:13,200
you can take everything into consideration

152
00:06:13,200 --> 00:06:15,260
and decide if you want to work with us.

153
00:06:16,280 --> 00:06:16,880
Right.

154
00:06:18,760 --> 00:06:19,960
As far as I know.

155
00:06:23,200 --> 00:06:24,960
We'll head back first, Mr. Li.

156
00:06:25,120 --> 00:06:26,520
We'll wait for your call.

157
00:06:29,200 --> 00:06:29,840
Let's go.

158
00:06:39,080 --> 00:06:40,140
Can you still walk?

159
00:06:40,680 --> 00:06:43,240
Did you see his expression just now?

160
00:06:43,760 --> 00:06:45,600
He turned pale from fear.

161
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:48,320
What did you say to him?

162
00:06:49,480 --> 00:06:52,159
I was at their branch this afternoon

163
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:53,640
chatting with the staff.

164
00:06:53,960 --> 00:06:54,960
I saw

165
00:06:55,159 --> 00:06:58,680
license plates from neighboring Tinghe County.

166
00:06:59,400 --> 00:07:02,800
The delivery boxes also had addresses from Tinghe County.

167
00:07:03,320 --> 00:07:03,920
But...

168
00:07:04,520 --> 00:07:06,450
Is there anything wrong with that?

169
00:07:07,280 --> 00:07:08,440
As far as I know...

170
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:10,920
Jiangda Express has clear regulations

171
00:07:10,960 --> 00:07:12,620
that individual contractors

172
00:07:12,640 --> 00:07:14,360
must operate within authorized specific areas.

173
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:17,360
Your station is at risk of cross-regional operation.

174
00:07:17,640 --> 00:07:19,240
I sincerely want to cooperate with you.

175
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:20,480
So I'm reminding you.

176
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:22,160
It's best to correct it as soon as possible

177
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:23,960
to avoid unnecessary losses.

178
00:07:24,400 --> 00:07:25,840
I was wondering

179
00:07:25,960 --> 00:07:28,240
if he was operating outside his area.

180
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:32,000
I didn't expect to be right.

181
00:07:34,320 --> 00:07:35,120
Slow down.

182
00:07:35,240 --> 00:07:36,400
You can't drink at all.

183
00:07:36,400 --> 00:07:37,520
Why did you compete in drinking with them?

184
00:07:37,520 --> 00:07:39,400
Who said I can't drink?

185
00:07:39,760 --> 00:07:40,920
Let me tell you.

186
00:07:41,080 --> 00:07:44,280
I've seen plenty of these drinking parties.

187
00:07:44,680 --> 00:07:47,159
I always win effortlessly.

188
00:07:47,320 --> 00:07:48,450
It's a piece of cake.

189
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:50,680
Slow down. Slow down.

190
00:07:51,080 --> 00:07:52,540
You can't do this anymore.

191
00:07:53,680 --> 00:07:55,920
Don't worry. I'm fine.

192
00:07:56,360 --> 00:07:57,560
Let me tell you.

193
00:07:57,840 --> 00:08:00,960
My alcohol tolerance is like a spring.

194
00:08:02,200 --> 00:08:03,600
I will absolutely

195
00:08:04,200 --> 00:08:07,080
never get drunk in front of others.

196
00:08:07,720 --> 00:08:10,600
Unless I feel truly safe,

197
00:08:10,760 --> 00:08:12,160
I won't dare to get drunk.

198
00:08:17,400 --> 00:08:19,260
You're not tough at all like this.

199
00:08:19,280 --> 00:08:21,680
You're just a little girl trying to hold on.

200
00:08:21,760 --> 00:08:23,020
After all these years.

201
00:08:23,880 --> 00:08:25,280
So this is how you made it through?
